com.github.robtimus.sql.function

Interface LongToDoubleSQLFunction

  • Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface LongToDoubleSQLFunction
    Represents a function that accepts a long-valued argument and produces a double-valued result. This is the SQLException throwing equivalent of LongToDoubleFunction.
